birthday.label: Birthday
birthday.webPage:
<webPage title="Add a rule">
  <init>
    <set dstPath="type" expr="type || 'absolute'" id="2937330475" type="enum"/>
    <set dstPath="precision" expr="precision || 'day'" id="2937330476" type="enum"/>
    <set dstPath="operator" expr="operator || 'eq'" id="2937330477" type="enum"/>
    <set dstPath="includeStart" expr="!!includeStart" id="2937330478" type="boolean"/>
    <set dstPath="includeEnd" expr="!!includeEnd" id="2937330479" type="boolean"/>
    <set dstPath="nextUnitsValue" expr="nextUnitsValue ? nextUnitsValue : 1" id="2937330480"
         type="number"/>
    <set dstPath="previousUnitsValue" expr="previousUnitsValue ? previousUnitsValue : 1"
         id="2937330481" type="number"/>
  </init>
  <canvas>
    <container id="2937330482">
      <text id="2937330483" style="medium"><![CDATA[Define the filtering conditions on the birth date.]]></text>
    </container>
    <container id="2937330484">
      <dropDown datePart="day" id="2937330485" label="Filter type" path="type"/>
      <dropDown datePart="day" id="2937330486" label="Level of precision" path="precision"/>
      <dropDown datePart="day" id="2937330487" label="Operator" path="operator" visibleIf="type === 'absolute'"/>
    </container>
    <container id="2937330488">
      <input datePart="day" id="2937330489" label="Date" path="day" visibleIf="type === 'absolute' && precision === 'day'"/>
      <input datePart="month" id="2937330490" label="Month" path="month" visibleIf="type === 'absolute' && precision === 'month'"/>
      <input datePart="day" id="2937330491" label="Start date" path="day" visibleIf="type === 'interval' && precision === 'day'"/>
      <input datePart="month" id="2937330492" label="Start month" path="month" visibleIf="type === 'interval' && precision === 'month'"/>
    </container>
    <container id="2937330493">
      <checkBox datePart="day" id="2937330494" label="Included" path="includeStart"
                visibleIf="type === 'interval'"/>
    </container>
    <container id="2937330495">
      <input datePart="day" id="2937330496" label="End date" path="endDay" visibleIf="type === 'interval' && precision === 'day'"/>
      <input datePart="month" id="2937330497" label="End month" path="endMonth" visibleIf="type === 'interval' && precision === 'month'"/>
    </container>
    <container id="2937330498">
      <checkBox datePart="day" id="2937330499" label="Included" path="includeEnd"
                visibleIf="type === 'interval'"/>
    </container>
    <container id="2937330500" layout="stackLeft" visibleIf="type === 'relative' && precision === 'day'">
      <container id="2937330501" valign="middle">
        <radioButton datePart="day" id="2937330502" label="Upcoming days" path="relativeValue"
                     valign="middle" value="nextUnits"/>
      </container>
      <input datePart="day" id="2937330503" noLabel="true" path="nextUnitsValue"/>
    </container>
    <container id="2937330504">
      <radioButton datePart="day" id="2937330505" label="Tomorrow" path="relativeValue"
                   value="next" visibleIf="type === 'relative' && precision === 'day'"/>
      <radioButton datePart="day" id="2937330506" label="Today" path="relativeValue"
                   value="current" visibleIf="type === 'relative' && precision === 'day'"/>
      <radioButton datePart="day" id="2937330507" label="Yesterday" path="relativeValue"
                   value="previous" visibleIf="type === 'relative' && precision === 'day'"/>
    </container>
    <container id="2937330508" layout="stackLeft" visibleIf="type === 'relative' && precision === 'day'">
      <container id="2937330509" valign="middle">
        <radioButton datePart="day" id="2937330510" label="Preceding days" path="relativeValue"
                     valign="middle" value="previousUnits"/>
      </container>
      <input datePart="day" id="2937330511" noLabel="true" path="previousUnitsValue"/>
    </container>
    <container id="2937330512" layout="stackLeft" visibleIf="type === 'relative' && precision === 'month'">
      <container id="2937330513" valign="middle">
        <radioButton datePart="day" id="2937330514" label="Upcoming months" path="relativeValue"
                     value="nextUnits"/>
      </container>
      <input datePart="day" id="2937330515" noLabel="true" path="nextUnitsValue"/>
    </container>
    <container id="2937330516">
      <radioButton datePart="day" id="2937330517" label="Next month" path="relativeValue"
                   value="next" visibleIf="type === 'relative' && precision === 'month'"/>
      <radioButton datePart="day" id="2937330518" label="This month" path="relativeValue"
                   value="current" visibleIf="type === 'relative' && precision === 'month'"/>
      <radioButton datePart="day" id="2937330519" label="Last month" path="relativeValue"
                   value="previous" visibleIf="type === 'relative' && precision === 'month'"/>
    </container>
    <container id="2937330520" layout="stackLeft" visibleIf="type === 'relative' && precision === 'month'">
      <container id="2937330521" valign="middle">
        <radioButton datePart="day" id="2937330522" label="Preceding months" path="relativeValue"
                     valign="middle" value="previousUnits"/>
      </container>
      <input datePart="day" id="2937330523" noLabel="true" path="previousUnitsValue"/>
    </container>
  </canvas>
</webPage>
